ABOUT

cellout is a very small program that prints battery status to STDOUT. It was
originally designed to be piped to dmenu(1) for use as a status bar battery
monitor.

OUTPUT

Output is in the format

    [BBBB] PPPS

where:

B - Battery charge. # equals 25% filled.
P - Percentage charged.
S - Battery state. Usually either C (Charging), D (Discharging), F (Full), or M (Missing).

